# Sourced by dpibypass. %TCP% / %UDP% are replaced with your configured ports.
STRATEGY_NAME="Fake + MultiSplit (default)"
STRATEGY_DESC="Injects a fake TLS packet, then splits the real one. Best all-round starting point; covers VLESS/Reality and Shadowsocks on TCP plus QUIC/Hysteria on UDP."
